UPDATE tasks
    SET
      task_status = ?,
      on_complete_batch_token = ?,
      on_complete_primary_media_file_token = ?,
      on_complete_primary_media_file_class = ?,
      on_complete_primary_media_file_cdn_url = ?,
      on_complete_primary_media_file_thumbnail_url_template = ?
    WHERE
      provider = ?
      AND provider_job_id = ?
